## ✅ VALIDATION RULES (2 marks each – implement ALL)

| Field Type         | Rule                                                                                          |
|--------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Name** (any field with “name” in key) | Letters + single spaces only, 2‑50 chars. Regex: `/^[A-Za-z]+( [A-Za-z]+)*$/` |
| **Username**       | 3‑20 chars, letters/numbers/underscore only. `/^[a-zA-Z0-9_]+$/`                             |
| **Password**       | min 8 chars, 1 uppercase, 1 lowercase, 1 number, 1 special char.                             |
| **Integer**        | Non‑negative integer (`>=0`, integer).                                                       |
| **Money (RWF)**    | Integer ≥0, display with `.toLocaleString()` + " RWF".                                       |
| **Date**           | Valid date string (required).                                                                |
| **Trim & Sanitise** | Every string: trim, strip HTML, collapse spaces.                                             |
| **Phone (if exists)** | Rwandan: `078/079/072/073` + 7 digits.                                                   |
| **Plate (if exists)** | Rwanda plate: `/^[A-Z]{1,3} \d{1,4}( [A-Z])?$/`                                         |

